You are developing a macOS menu bar app called iStatBar (GitHub: leebo/istatbar) located at /home/ubuntu/projects/istatbar.

The current code is a basic skeleton. Your task is to implement a FULL iStat Menu-style detailed panel view.

## Current State
- Basic menu bar item with CPU/Memory/Disk/Network display
- 1-second update timer
- Basic system stats collection

## What to Build

### 1. Detailed Panel Window
When user clicks the menu bar icon, show a native macOS panel (NSPopover or NSWindow) with:
- **CPU Section**: Usage percentage, small usage graph
- **Memory Section**: Used/Buffered/Cached breakdown, percentage
- **Disk Section**: Read/write speeds for each volume
- **Network Section**: Real-time upload/download speed graph
- **System Info**: Uptime, model name, macOS version

### 2. Requirements
- Use AppKit only (no SwiftUI)
- All stats update every 1 second
- Menu bar shows condensed info: "CPU: 23% | Mem: 8.2G | Net: ↓12M"
- Panel should look polished like iStat Menu - dark theme, clean typography
- Use NSStatusItem with custom NSView for the menu bar button (not just text)
- Support Retina displays

### 3. Project Structure to Create/Update
```
Sources/
├── App/
│   ├── main.swift
│   └── AppDelegate.swift
├── MenuBar/
│   ├── MenuBarController.swift      (update to show panel)
│   ├── StatusBarView.swift          (custom menu bar view)
│   └── DetailPanelWindow.swift      (the popover panel)
├── Views/
│   ├── CPUView.swift
│   ├── MemoryView.swift
│   ├── DiskView.swift
│   ├── NetworkView.swift
│   └── SystemInfoView.swift
├── Models/
│   ├── SystemMonitor.swift          (extend existing)
│   ├── CPUMonitor.swift
│   ├── MemoryMonitor.swift
│   ├── DiskMonitor.swift
│   └── NetworkMonitor.swift
└── Utils/
    └── Extensions.swift
```

### 4. Important
- Run `xcodegen generate` after changing project.yml
- Test that the build succeeds: `xcodebuild -project iStatBar.xcodeproj -scheme iStatBar -configuration Debug build CODE_SIGN_IDENTITY="-" CODE_SIGNING_REQUIRED=NO`
- Commit each significant change with clear commit messages
- Push commits to main branch

When done, run: openclaw system event --text "iStatBar development complete" --mode now
